Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Perform up to 4 Slash attacks forward, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
When executing the 4th attack, recall all swords on the field and deploy 6 swords.

Hold <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Rapidly unleash multiple Sword Aura while continuously consuming <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color>, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
Attack duration can be extended by repeatedly pressing or holding;
When hitting enemies, increases CRIT Rate by 6% for 60s, stacks up to 5 times, can gain 1 stack every 0.1s, repeated triggers reset the duration.

While in <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance]</color> and on the ground, press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Perform up to two slashes forward, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
When hitting enemies, gain 1 stack of <color=#FFFFFF>[Sky Force]</color> effect.

After the second hit of <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Sword Stance - Earth]</color>, press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Perform a slash forward, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
After release, press <IconMap:Icon_Special> to Quick Launch <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Sword Stance - Heaven Style Third Form]</color>;
Upon activating this skill, if hit by an enemy attack, can trigger Block effect, gain immunity to that DMG, and gain 2 stacks of <color=#FFFFFF>[Sky Force]</color>.

When released with <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color>, perform a large area slash forward, dealing massive <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
When hitting enemies, consumes 1 point of <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color> and gains 2 stacks of <color=#FFFFFF>[Sky Force]</color>, meanwhile consumes all <color=#FFFFFF>[Sky Force]</color> stacks, increasing this skill's DMG based on <color=#FFFFFF>[Core Passive]</color> skill Lv.

After triggering Perfect Dodge during <color=#FFFFFF>[Dash Attack: Retraction Slash]</color>, press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Perform a slash forward, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
After release, press <IconMap:Icon_Special> to Quick Launch <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Sword Stance - Heaven Style Third Form]</color>;
Upon activating this skill, if hit by an enemy attack, can trigger Block effect, gain immunity to that DMG, and gain 2 stacks of <color=#FFFFFF>[Sky Force]</color>, stacking up to 4 times;

When released with <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color>, perform a large area slash forward, dealing massive <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
When hitting enemies, consumes 1 point of <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color> and gains 2 stacks of <color=#FFFFFF>[Sky Force]</color>, meanwhile consumes all <color=#FFFFFF>[Sky Force]</color> stacks, increasing this skill's DMG based on <color=#FFFFFF>[Core Passive]</color> skill Lv.

While in <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance]</color> and in mid-air, press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Perform up to two downward slashes forward, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
When hitting enemies, gain 1 stack of <color=#FFFFFF>[Sky Force]</color> effect.

After the second hit of <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Sword Stance - Heaven]</color>, press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Perform a plunging attack downward, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
After release, press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to Quick Launch <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Sword Stance - Earth Style Third Form]</color>;
Upon activating this skill, if hit by an enemy attack, can trigger Block effect, gain immunity to that DMG, and gain 2 stacks of <color=#FFFFFF>[Sky Force]</color> effect.

When released with <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color>, perform a large area plunging attack downward, dealing massive <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
When hitting enemies, consumes 1 point of <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color> and gains 2 stacks of <color=#FFFFFF>[Sky Force]</color> effect, meanwhile consumes all <color=#FFFFFF>[Sky Force]</color> stacks to increase skill DMG, with the specific increase scaling with <color=#FFFFFF>[Core Passive]</color> skill Lv.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Evade> to activate:
A quick dash dodge;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill;
In <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance]</color>, after triggering a Perfect Dodge, press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to quickly launch <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Sword Stance - Earth]</color>.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Special> to activate:
If there are swords on the field when activated, quickly step on the nearest sword and launch a swift Sword Aura attack against enemies, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
If there are no swords on the field when activated, the activation fails;
Upon successful activation, can quickly chain into <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Sword Aura]</color>;
During activation, swords on the field will be collected and converted into <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color>.

Hold <IconMap:Icon_Special> to activate:
If there are swords on the field when activated, quickly step on the nearest sword and, after a brief charge, perform a dash slash and Sword Aura attack dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
If there are no swords on the field when activated, the skill fails;
After release, can quickly chain into the third hit of <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack]</color>; leaves 2 swords on the field;
During activation, collects swords on the field and converts them into <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color>.

With enough energy, hold <IconMap:Icon_SpecialReady> to activate:
If swords exist on the field when activated, quickly step on the nearest sword and, after a brief charge, perform a dash slash and Sword Aura attack, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
If no swords exist on the field when activated, the activation fails; During activation, swords on the field will be collected and converted into <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color>; After release, can quickly chain into the third hit of <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack]</color>, and leave 5 swords on the field;
After activation, gain <color=#FFFFFF>[Terrain]</color> effect. While in <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance]</color>, using <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance - Earth Style Third Form]</color> will automatically Ascend to <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance - Earth Secret Art]</color>, lasting until <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance]</color> ends.

After <color=#FFFFFF>[EX Special Attack: Sword Stance - Flash]</color>, when <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color> is depleted, press or hold <IconMap:Icon_SpecialReady> to trigger:
Dealing massive <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color> to enemies in a large area;
After using this skill, deactivate <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Evil Slayer]</color> and exit <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance]</color>

In <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance]</color>, when a <color=#FFFFFF>[Chain Attack]</color> is triggered, select the character to activate:
Unleashes a powerful slash at enemies ahead in a large area, dealing massive <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

When Decibel Rating is at <color=#FFFFFF>[Maximum]</color>, press <IconMap:Icon_UltimateReady> to activate:
Summon a Sword Stanceation, dealing massive <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
After using this skill, activates <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Evil Slayer]</color> to enter <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance]</color>, and gains 4 <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Will]</color>. Both <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance]</color> and <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Evil Slayer]</color> last for 12 seconds;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> after a <color=#FFFFFF>Defensive Assist</color> to activate:
Deals massive <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

While in <color=#FFFFFF>[Sword Stance]</color>, press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> after a <color=#FFFFFF>[Defensive Assist]</color> to activate:
Deal massive <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

